@api-key = your-api-key-1
@api-version = 1.0.0
@user-id = alice

### AI Route Recommendations - Basic Keyword Search
POST http://localhost:4000/ai/routes/recommendations
x-api-key: {{api-key}}
accept-version: {{api-version}}
x-user-id: {{user-id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keywords": ["waterfall"],
  "mode": "any",
  "region": "Bungo Ono",
  "proximityRadiusKm": 200,
  "maxRoutes": 2,
  "minSpotsPerCluster": 1
}

